{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "爱德华 第1话 完美的管家",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "请问一下，\\n尤蒂尔大人\\n在这座城堡里吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我就是\\n尤蒂尔……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "失礼了。\\n我名叫爱德华。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "能请您\\n雇佣我担任管家吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "管家？\\n不，我们现在不需要……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "诶，管家吗。\\n具体会帮我们做哪些事啊？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "如果尤蒂尔同意，\\n你也能帮我们做事吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "哇！？\\n你们什么时候……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "只要主人有此意愿，\\n我自然会帮助诸位。\\n不过，这取决于我能否被雇佣。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "真的吗！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "喂，尤蒂尔！\\n雇佣他吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "管理武器啊，修补城堡之类的事，\\n老实说真的很麻烦。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "我同意。\\n我想找人帮我管理食材，掌握库存。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "情况就是这样，\\n您意下如何？\\n尤蒂尔大人。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯……好的，既然大家都希望的话。\\n我就雇佣你吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "非常感谢您愿意雇佣我。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "那事不宜迟，请让我确认一下\\n尤蒂尔大人今天的安排吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "嗯……连一半都还没完成呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "那就请您在用午餐之前\\n完成训练和周边的巡视。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "诶……但是，我肚子饿了，\\n想先吃午饭……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "这可不行。安排在上午的工作\\n必须在中午之前完成。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "午后还要出城消灭魔兽呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "诶，这样一来，\\n不就几乎没时间吃饭了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "那是因为您没能尽快\\n完成安排在上午的工作。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "明天起我会好好为您\\n腾出享用午餐的时间，请放心。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不，但是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "雇佣我担任管家的，\\n不正是您吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "唔……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "今后，我照顾您生活起居的同时，\\n也会判断您作为我的主人\\n是否够格。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "无需担心，今后\\n我将安排好您的一切事务。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "想必您很快就会成为\\n一名值得我侍奉的主人。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "当然，前提是\\n您没有中途放弃。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "那个……。\\n库、库菈乌。兰扎卜……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "哎呀，那个，果然自己的工作\\n就得由自己来管理呢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "好了，我这就去完成修补城堡的工作！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "我也是，不需要别人帮忙。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "仔细想想，其实库存管理之类的，\\n一个人也完全可以胜任。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "怎、怎么这样……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "走吧，尤蒂尔大人。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "不能再浪费时间了。\\n立即开始工作吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}